T1  - Public health impacts of city policies to reduce climate change: findings from the URGENCHE EU-China project.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1186/s12940-016-0097-0
A1  - Sabel, Clive E
A1  - Hiscock, Rosemary
A1  - Asikainen, Arja
A1  - Bi, Jun
A1  - Depledge, Mike
A1  - van den Elshout, Sef
