T1  - Modelling and estimation of HIV prevalence and number of people living with HIV in India, 2010-2011.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1177/0956462415612650
A1  - Raj, Yujwal
A1  - Sahu, Damodar
A1  - Pandey, Arvind
A1  - Venkatesh, S
A1  - Reddy, Dcs
A1  - Bakkali, Taoufik
A1  - Das, Chinmoyee
A1  - Singh, Kh Jitenkumar
A1  - Kant, Shashi
A1  - Bhattacharya, M
A1  - Stover, John
