T1  - Evolution of Socioeconomic Conditions and Its Relation to Spatial-Temporal Changes of Giardiasis and Helminthiasis in Amazonian Children.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1007/s10393-016-1167-z
A1  - Delfino, B M
A1  - Campos, R G
