T1  - Tuberculosis Among Temporary Visa Holders Working in the Tourism Industry - United States, 2012-2014.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.15585/mmwr.mm6511a3
A1  - Weinberg, Meghan P
A1  - Cherry, Cara
A1  - Lipnitz, Julie
