T1  - Computer-assisted quantification of motile and invasive capabilities of cancer cells.
T3  - Erratum in: Sci Rep. 2018 Jul 02;8:46996. doi: 10.1038/srep46996. PMID: 29961773 [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/29961773] Erratum in: Sci Rep. 2025 Jul 2;15(1):23572. doi: 10.1038/s41598-025-09573-z. PMID: 40603559 [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/40603559]
