T1  - Investigation of a Measles Outbreak in China to Identify Gaps in Vaccination Coverage, Routes of Transmission, and Interventions.
T3  - Erratum in: PLoS One. 2016 Dec 9;11(12):e0168222. doi: 10.1371/journal.pone.0168222 PMID: 27936207 [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/27936207]
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1371/journal.pone.0133983
A1  - Zheng, Xiang
A1  - Zhang, Ningjing
A1  - Zhang, Xiaoshu
A1  - Hao, Lixin
A1  - Su, Qiru
