T1  - Prevalence of hypertension at high altitude: cross-sectional survey in Ladakh, Northern India 2007-2011.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1136/bmjopen-2014-007026
A1  - Norboo, Tsering
A1  - Stobdan, Tsering
A1  - Tsering, Norboo
A1  - Angchuk, Norboo
