T1  - Travel-associated sexually transmitted infections: an observational cross-sectional study of the GeoSentinel surveillance database.
T3  - Comment in: Lancet Infect Dis. 2013 Mar;13(3):184-5. doi: 10.1016/S1473-3099(12)70271-2. PMID: 23182930 [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23182930] Comment in: Lancet Infect Dis. 2013 Aug;13(8):651-2. doi: 10.1016/S1473-3099(13)70180-4. PMID: 23886325 [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23886325] Comment in: Lancet Infect Dis. 2013 Aug;13(8):651. doi: 10.1016/S1473-3099(13)70106-3. PMID: 23886326 [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23886326]
