T1  - Domestic radon exposure and risk of childhood cancer: a prospective census-based cohort study.
T3  - Erratum in: Environ Health Perspect. 2013 Oct;121(10):1244
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1289/ehp.1306500
A1  - Hauri, Dimitri
A1  - Spycher, Ben
A1  - Huss, Anke
A1  - Zimmermann, Frank
A1  - Grotzer, Michael
A1  - von der Weid, Nicolas
