T1  - [Role of socio-economy and management in sustainable transmission control of schistosomiasis in Taoyuan County, Hunan Province, China].
A1  - Luo, Zhi-Hong
A1  - Li, Sheng-Ming
A1  - Zhou, Xiao-Nong
A1  - Yi, Ping
A1  - Ren, Guang-Hui
A1  - Franziska, Bieri
