T1  - Factors associated with degree of atopy in Latino children in a nationwide pediatric sample: the Genes-environments and Admixture in Latino Asthmatics (GALA II) study.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.jaci.2013.02.046
A1  - Kumar, Rajesh
